---
title: Fajita-Inspired Beef Flatbreads with Sour Cream Sauce and Cheddar Cheese
description: We're reimagining family favourite fajitas as a no-fuss flatbread meal! Quick-cooking ground beef and peppers are seasoned with Tex-Mex paste and nestled atop toasted flatbreads, finished with gooey cheddar cheese and a drizzle of sour cream sauce.
